nerator-feed</span><br><span class="line">- hexo-generator-sitemap</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="安装pacman主题_github地址">安装pacman主题 <a href="https://github.com/A-limon/pacman" target="_blank" rel="external">github地址</a></h3><h4 id="安装_(切换到博客目录)">安装 (切换到博客目录)</h4><figure class="highlight groovy"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git clone <span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//github.com/A-limon/pacman.git themes/pacman</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
